com.hp.hpl.jena.query
Interface DatasetAccessor

All Known Implementing Classes:
DatasetAdapter
public interface DatasetAccessor

Accessor to a dataset as a collection of models, providing whole model operations. Models can be added, remopve and replaced. This interface provides a uniform interface to local and remote datasets and is based on SPARQL 1.1 Graph Store HTTP Protocol. The factory methods in DatasetAccessorFactory provides creators for DatasetAccessors to local and remote (over HTTP) data. local na dremote
